Sri Lanka to Grow at 8% on Moderate Inflation, Jayasundera Says

-- B y   A n u s h a   O n d a a t j i e   a n d   A s a n t h a   S i r i m a n n e
-- 
2011-07-04T05:03:36Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/sri-lanka-to-grow-at-8-on-moderate-inflation-jayasundera-says.html
Sri Lanka  aims to grow at 8 percent
with moderate inflation after increasing investments in ports,
roads and power, Treasury Secretary P.B. Jayasundera said.  The South Asian island is on track to achieve a budget
deficit of 7 percent this year, he said at a business forum in
 Colombo  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Anusha Ondaatjie in Colombo at 
 anushao@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
